Title: Relates to the practice of acupuncture and certain exemptions
Summary: Relates to the practice of acupuncture and the exemption that a person who does not otherwise possess the credentials or qualifications required for the practice of acupuncture may be trained by the National Acupuncture Detoxification Association (NADA), or other equivalent.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the education law, in relation to the practice of acupuncture and certain exemptions
